Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a cliff up ahead. If we\Nkeep going like this, it'll be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay inside the guard rails.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}20 years after the date of my birth,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came face to face \Nwith true darkness for the first time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No worries, no worries. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear viewers, might you be aware{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that large numbers of honeybees\Nare said to be disappearing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do I ask? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because this nighttime orienteering\Ndeep in the mountains unfolding before you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is due to my own disappearance as a worker bee.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Ozu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water over here tastes lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water over there tastes bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh heh, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk to the next train stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that'll be for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is truly hell, and it's all that honey's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or rather, it's all because \Nof my total infatuation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is responsible? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Probably me. Just this time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:26.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tatami Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I was a freshmen university student{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and before me lay open countless\Ndoors to that rose-colored campus life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Softball Circle Honwaka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:08.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Recruiting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems that Honwaka reserves a corner of\Nthe sports field each week and plays softball,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with the occasional game thrown in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other than that it's totally free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The logo might say "softball circle,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it looks like their main purpose is\Nto engage in warm-hearted intermingling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here there is no practicing day\Nand night chasing around white balls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no sweat, no tears, no guts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one is aiming for any national tournament...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Farewell, my melancholic high school days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would not be so bad to join with this bunch,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and while breaking into an invigorating\Nsweat, make a hundred friends!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will surely master cordial conversation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}while playing catch with beautiful\Nwomen during early morning practice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is an ability that I must master\Nto make my mark on this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is most definitely not simply\Nbecause I wish to converse with pretty girls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to learn the art! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if, after mastering the art,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a beautiful woman wished to come\Nwith me, I would have no reason to decline.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No worries... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fear not, and come to me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:11.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Softball Circle Honwaka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unfortunately I was an\Nidiot beyond all redemption.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, please listen carefully to\Nthe circumstances which befell me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I will accept no\Nleaving in the middle of this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The softball circle Honwaka\Nwas just as the name says.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like the covering clouds of a\Nspringtime haze, warm and snuggly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The thing that interested me the\Nmost was their male/female ratio.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please, eat! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's an organic sandwich\Nand tea with royal jelly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's most definitely not that I judge\Neverything primarily by such a criterion,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but was not this the best possible ratio\Nto nurture intimacy with the opposite sex?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only thing that worried me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...was that it was a bit too "warm and snuggly."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To put it simply, everyone was far too nice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That place doesn't use much pesticide, but\Nthe prices are quite reasonable, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idea of getting ducks to eat\Nharmful insects is quite effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The consumer shouldn't have\Nto suffer just because something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is more convenient for the producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People should at least have options.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They take away the people's choice\Nbecause they don't want them to get money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes you feel\Nlike a cup ramen, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the ones that\Nare bad for you with lots of oil...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think adults have to set a proper example.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can show the right attitude to the\Nchildren, then our children will grow up normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that children who are loved\Nproperly from a young age don't go astray.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could cross the street on a red light,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to teach them the concept of not\Nblindly accepting the law without question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before long I was no\Nlonger part of the conversation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and every time I uttered a word {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}everyone would fall silent with kind\Nsmiles still plastered on their faces.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Among those constantly brightly\Nsmiling faces, with no dissent or dirty talk,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was a single man I felt close to\Nnamed Ozu with a face like a youkai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With his peculiar conversational skills he\Nmanaged to secure his place within the circle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but he seemed to have trouble\Nsmiling and laughing innocently.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Giving the impression of an evil that\Ncould not be hidden lurking inside his gut,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he had a laugh so unnatural it was like he\Nwasn't born with the proper muscles to do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They say a drowning\Nman will even grasp at straw,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I immediately hit it off\Nwith such a slippery fellow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's everyone's fault for\Ncreating such a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who could learn the\N art of pleasant sociability {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}through such lukewarm interaction?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My patience had almost worn through.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a situation that could explode\Nat any time, like the Cuban Missile Crisis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, while I remained on the brink\None day in the summer of my freshman year,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had a fateful encounter which\Nmelted my heart in a warm embrace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her beauty was incredible. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt like her "whoa"\Nfactor was of 100% purity,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}like if you tried to speak with her\Nshe'd be too bright to look at directly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seemed she was an\Nimportant member of Honwaka,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and she was surrounded by people,\Nsmiling as she listened to their conversation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed the state exam\Nthanks to the royal jelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grades rose thanks to\Nthose concentration patches!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Honwaka\Nthat I've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was the personification of the\Nraven-haired maiden I pictured in my mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I walked with her along the\Nmall of Sanjoukawara or something,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet people would surely be jealous looking at\Nthe fresh young couple walking down the road.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look at you. Should you be\Neating something so unhealthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Neko Ramen is a mysterious food cart\Nthat only appears around Tadasu Forest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's rumored they use actual cats to\Nmake the broth, but there's no proof of it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The owner says it started living nearby\Nafter he began feeding it used bonito flakes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but if he was ever reported the police\NI'm sure his cart would be shut down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, the taste is unmatched.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kohinata-{\i1}san {\i0}is a freshman like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me, I can\Ntell what you are thinking at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear she's the only daughter\Nof the health food company
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's the umbrella group for Honwaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The softball circle Honwaka is a branch\Nof the health food company Honwaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she is the company's poster-child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, she doesn't have much enthusiasm\Nfor PR work, and only appears once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,\NI've never seen her play softball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may have shown up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you want to see her regularly,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems like you need to raise\Nyour position to a more suitable level.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At Honwaka, your rank in the circle\Nrises the more you buy their products.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With a high rank you can attend\Nmeetings only for high-ranked members,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that seemed like it'd\Nraise my chances of meeting her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:09:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you want to run along\Nthe path of love, I can't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. Who would go buying\Nhealth food products for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that like saying she's some grand prize\Nyou can win if you collect enough box tops?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, 30 portions of\Nsupplements and health drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really working hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Royal jelly is produced by the worker\Nbees after ingesting pollen they've collected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Its rarity causes the\Nproduction cost to skyrocket.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I first heard the\Ncost I thought it was a scam,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but when I heard how it was\Nmade I realized it wasn't some fraud,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and comparing the price with\Nother companies it seemed about right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only problem was that my own economic\Nsituation became somewhat unbalanced.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the time I had to sleep disappeared,\Nand I had to work day and night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if it's high quality stuff,\Njust eating it all at once will,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}on the contrary, be bad for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you take a lot, then any more\Nthan the set portion won't be absorbed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the rest will just wash\Nout of your system, or so I heard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thinking about that, I was\Nafraid of going to the bathroom,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for it was sure to leave\Nbehind precious nutrition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you got sick because\Nyou didn't take these!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My grandpa's illness got\Nbetter when I gave them to him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to the health food, my\Nlifestyle got more and more unhealthy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although it's thought that\Nhealthy food leads to good health,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}perhaps I would have been just as\Nhealthy if I had done nothing but sleep.{\i0}
