Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wholer Certificate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Plighter Certificate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Bee Missionary
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Healthy honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey candy for your health!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't be surprised, but two years had passed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I hadn't seen her even once since that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to obtain happiness quickly more\Nthan health, the environment, or world order...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How incredibly wasted \Nwere these past two years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no looking back on the incredible\Namount of money I earned and then spent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be healthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirm with the barcode.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the page is deleted,\Nthen it's an attack from someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This honey candy will protect you from the flu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that was discovered by NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were told not to tell anyone\Nbefore it was announced, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you mustn't believe\Neverything you read on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd like to just inform my dear\Nviewers: this is definitely not my style.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if you question my credibility, there's\Nnothing to look into and I have no answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finally, the strain of these\Ntwo years caused me to snap.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They say tourists walking down Shinkyougoku\Ncould hear that business was booming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trying to run from people's prying eyes,\Nbefore I knew it I had come to Kiyamachi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there an old fortune\Nteller was emitting an eerie aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was sure she wouldn't give\Nme any concrete advice, though.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are wrapped in unease, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! I didn't ask for\Na consultation or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense you have much talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I took off my helmet to\Nthe old woman's keen insight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could tell it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I feel there's an\Nopportunity you can't let pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab the opportunity that\Nis dangling in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 5,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I received the invitation to the national\Nassembly I'd been waiting and waiting for!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The national assembly is said to\Nbe a two day, two night ceremony{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}deep in the mountains at Honwaka's headquarters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please remove your blindfolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the nucleus of Honwaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,built with the latest\N technology and techniques,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is being targeted by spies even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take all care to keep\Nwhat you see and hear to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We left our luggage in our rooms\Nand headed to tour the factory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where we make the\Ncandy does not use any machinery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is 100% done by\Nhand, with no additives of any sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To create something wonderful,\Nit must be done by hand, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't look like 100% to me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Less than 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was then that a flag about 3 tatami in size\Nemblazoned with "Danger!" was unfurled within me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that we had a\Nperfunctory friendly softball game{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and then went around the \Norganic farm and beehives.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those that try to stop\Nus for their own crooked profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think we can lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:13:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that the righteous\Nwill be blessed in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all did great getting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you all got some funny looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like when you had\Npatches stuck on your forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's odd because it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The unbelievers can't taste\Nthe amazing power of nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all have found salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is still much work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are approaching a time when the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Global Warming
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cannot recover \Nfrom the illness inflicted upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozone Layer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:26.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Declining Birthrate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:27.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sexless
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:28.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Earthquakes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time of judgment is coming. 2012.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:29.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Natural Disasters
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:29.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Abnormal Weather
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prepare for the upcoming calamity,\Nwe have prepared our "Ark of Salvation."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll put a pair of each animal inside it,\Nand one pair of man and woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's basically Noah's Ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two people will board that flying ship\Nand will live on through the catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after the destruction is complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they will once again set foot on\Nthis earth and create a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:14:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad the world\Ncan't go on like it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I always worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, someone asks:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Are you worried about the\Nfinal judgment that's coming?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No, that's not it," I reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even though the situation will be so hopeless,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what really causes me\Ndespair is the number of people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that do not change to a new way of thinking."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we only have a small,\Ninsignificant amount of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we must continue\Nour efforts until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The souls of those who struggle to\Nthe end without their wishes fulfilled
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will quickly return home to the Pleiades.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After our bodies are destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our free souls will be reborn as new\Nlife-forms and ascend to a new, higher stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no need to worry\Nabout this troubling human life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, let me introduce my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:20.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Become a Person
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, it seems you\Nhaven't opened your hearts yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't continue to the next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless you spill out everything from the\Nbottom of your heart and confront your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you all just lived superficially?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your life hasn't gone so well,\Nthat's probably the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of my friends are successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they show their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truly great all understand this concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast out what you feel\Nfrom the bottom of your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always going on about\Na diet while stuffing your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always thought your hairstyle was gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:16:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you don't need a girlfriend,\Nbut you're just unpopular, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had plastic surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have 5,000,000 in my bank account!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gone out with more than\N200 people other than my boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wear a hairpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't love someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I throw up at family movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in crushing debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's untalented!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a mess on the toilet seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in it for the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eww! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody ever loved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all work together toward our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're family of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ugly world, here there is true love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my room later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you'll need some special guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:17:00.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Emotion, Victim, Devotion, Friendship, Pure, Faith,\NService, Effort, Health, Love, Hide Nothing, Reality
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite the spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently someone had\Nsomehow hijacked the ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're running, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so we slipped into\Nthe dark forest to run away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the next stop along the tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There were even more\Npeople after us at the next station.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:18:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it seemed there were some\Nnon-Honwaka people mixed in, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, one to\Nwarm you up, good customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't inquire about the details, but it seems\Nthis was the suggestion of one Master Higuchi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Neko Ramen then was especially delicious,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and as I slurped it up, tears fell from my eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was that worldly flavor I had missed so.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I decided then and there {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that even if the world were being destroyed\Ntomorrow, I would take myself to Neko Ramen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, please stop there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go down the canal to the Kamo River.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in women's clothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me with such a scary face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm lonely and the river breeze is chilly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lonely bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu, what in the world have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You head to the boarding house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have some minor\Nbusiness to take care of!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Akashi. I've brought\Na castella from the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master is here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems things are over. It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Ozu's evil deeds until\Nnow have all been exposed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and as a consequence he was thrown\Noff the Kamo-oohashi and broke his leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is one incorrigible fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. He's a slippery one to pin down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:20:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he said that he'd\Ncover for you, come what may.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your book, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finished reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this seems to be yours as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used it unknowingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a book I bought at a used book fair.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought Ozu had borrowed it and never\Nreturned it, but I guess this Master read it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's been more than a year since then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in trouble if there are fewer bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there'll be an increase in moths.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Clear-headed, in the engineering department,\Nand smart enough to design airplanes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akashi-san seemed to have no fear,\Nexcept when it came to moths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She told me she was\Nsearching for her lost Mochiguman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This opportunity is dangling\Nright in front of your eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it! I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in this crazy stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because it'd be really scary if it were true!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How did something like this happen?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Greater than the love Hikaru Genji\Nfelt for his infant daughter Kaguya,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt fear the likes of\Nwhich I'd never felt before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this rate, would I not have\Nbeen happier staying with Honwaka?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I had thrown away these past two years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must face this reality\Nhead on, with conviction!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
